static

This symbol is the offset where the com.google.android.gms.R.attr#actionBarSize attribute's value can be found in the AppCompatTheme array.

      <p>May be a dimension value, which is a floating point number appended with a unit such as "<code>14.5sp</code>".

Available units are: px (pixels), dp (density-independent pixels), sp (scaled pixels based on preferred font size), in (inches), mm (millimeters).
